# UI.Vision Macro Rules

## Naming Conventions
- Use descriptive names for macros
- Prefix test macros with "test_"
- Use snake_case for macro names

## Structure
- Group related commands using comments
- Keep macros focused on a single task
- Use variables for reusable values

## Error Handling
- Include error checking where appropriate
- Use "!ERRORIGNORE" only when necessary
- Add timeout handling for UI interactions